Algorithmic attribution
-----------------------

This repository implements the trellis-coded quantization algorithms
described in QTIP (Tseng et al., NeurIPS 2024), adapted to per-expert
Hessian calibration for the OLMoE-1B-7B mixture-of-experts architecture.

    QTIP paper:   https://arxiv.org/abs/2406.11235
    QTIP code:    https://github.com/Cornell-RelaxML/qtip (GPL-3.0)

The code under src/ (codebooks, Viterbi encoder, BlockLDLQ, CUDA
kernels, OLMoE adapter, calibration pipeline, evaluation harness) is
an independent clean-room implementation of the algorithms described
in the QTIP paper. No source code from the upstream QTIP repository
is used, linked, or redistributed here; the GPL-3.0 license of the
upstream QTIP project therefore does not transitively apply to this
work.

